project_descr: United Nations Joint Programme (UNJP) aims to facilitate Cambodian young people to labor force while reducing in equalities particularly for disadvantaged and vulnerable group-and ensure young women and men are better able to meet labor demand.

outputs.output_descr: Young women and men access quality formal and non-formal education increasingly obtain decent and productive employment opportunities.
